snippet.title: Sincognito: Teaser Trailer (Social Deduction, Physics, Horror Game)
snippet.description:
Wishlist & Request Playtest: Play online on Steam or play Solo against the crafty AI: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2174060?utm_source=YouTube&utm_campaign=ScreamFest2024&utm_medium=web

Sincognito is a social deduction, stealth, physics based horror game based on the 7 Deadly Sins - Play with 7 unique playstyles as the personified Sins or play as Humans to deduce who the secret Sin is!

Join us on Discord & Help grow our Community: https://discord.gg/3UQ88n8uDm

Our studio's website: https://www.knockbackgames.co.uk/ 

Other links (Tiktok, Twitter, Reddit, etc.): https://linktr.ee/knockbackgames

------- 

We really appreciate your support, we're a small studio of 3 indie developers without any publishers and it'll greatly help us grow and develop if you can Like, Comment, Share & Subscribe - If you do any of these it'll greatly help us. 

We're eager to see where Sincognito in its current alpha stage goes from here, join us now!!
